'''Isgaarsiinta''' ({{lang-en|Telecommunication}}; {{lang-ar|اتصال عن بعد}}) waa diritaanka iyo helitaanka astaamaha, signalada, fariimaha, qoraalada, [[sawir]]aanta, codka, maqalka iyo muuqaaka taasi oo loo adeegsanayo aalado leh xadhko, raadiyow, elektaromagnetik iyo nidaamyo kale.<ref>{{citation |publisher=[[International Telecommunication Union]] |title=[[ITU Radio Regulations]] |chapter=Article 1.3 |chapter-url=http://www.itu.int/dms_pub/itu-s/oth/02/02/S02020000244501PDFE.PDF |date=2012}}</ref><ref>Constitution and Convention of the International Telecommunication Union, Annex (Geneva, 1992)</ref> 
Isgaarsiinta caalamku maanta waxay maraysaa heerkii ugu sareeyay ee abid [[dad]]ku gaadhaan.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://education.yahoo.com/reference/dictionary/entry/telecommunication |title=Definition of telecommunication |work=Yahoo |accessdate=28 February 2013 |ciwaan=Nuqul Archive |archive-date=1 May 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501055117/http://education.yahoo.com/reference/dictionary/entry/telecommunication |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/telecommunication |title=Telecommunication  |work= Collins English Dictionary |accessdate=28 February 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.vocabulary.com/dictionary/telecommunication |title=Telecommunication |work= Vocabulary.com |accessdate=28 February 2013}}</ref>

==Hordhac==
Isgaarsiintu waa isgaarsiin elekroon ah oo meel dheer la iskala xariiri karo. Waxyaabaha Isgaarsiinta waxaa ka mid ah [[Taleefoon]]ada, [[Radio|Raadiyaha]], [[Telefishin|talefishinada]] iyo [[Kombuyuutar]]ada.Isgaarsiinta waxee maanta ka midtahay kuwa ugu muhiimsan dhaqaalaha Caalamka.

